data.description: ENJOY THE COUNTRY SETTING FEELING WHILE HAVING ALL THE AMENTIES OF CITY LIMITS! This 3-bedroom 2 full bath home sets on .64 acres m/l with 3 outbuildings and 1 shop building. Shop building is 30x36, full size attic and electric, plenty of room for parking, storage or workshop. Additional buildings can be used for insulated storage, lawn storage and so much more. Home has large living room and large entry room that could be used as office or large mud room. Updated double pane vinyl windows, metal roof and some original wood floors throughout. Property is being sold "AS-IS" but has so much to offer, come take a look while it last!
